description:
This is a 14 minute workout called 'The Ultimate Stretching Routine After Any Workout (Post Workout Routine)' from the channel Breathe and Flow.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching and Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Welcome to this ultimate stretching routine ideal post workout for example weight lifting, martial arts, running, surfing or really any other activity. Take the time to slow down after your training to shift into and activate a relaxed & digest state of the nervous system - the parasympathetic state. Do this after every training in a quiet spot. Rest well and grow stronger! Flo from Breathe and Flow is teaching this class.
